data.title: Oregon ZIP Code - United States
data.meta_description: To find out the Oregon ZIP code you have to select a city (Abmps, Adair Village, Adams, Adel, Adrian, Agate Beach, Agness, Albany, Allegany, Aloha, Alpine, Alsea, Alvadore, Amity, Antelope, Applegate, Arcadia, Arch Cape, Arlington, Arock, Ashland, etc.) and then you will see all the postal codes for this city according to the area.
data.text:
The state Oregon has 486 different ZIP Codes among its 582 distinct locations. The postal code range goes from 97001 to 97920. Search for the location name or search inside the map below.

Oregon ZIP Codes Areas

If the map does not load automatically, press the load button on the upper right corner. You can amplify the map to search for an address.

Choose a city
